      'news.eug.h4a': 'Energy Management Solutions',
      'news.eug.p1': '<strong>SimDyns Technology Solutions</strong> has been awarded the prestigious <strong>EU SeeBridge grant</strong> to develop a cutting-edge energy management solution. This initiative focuses on enhancing <strong>energy efficiency</strong> through advanced technologies and sustainable practices, aligning with the EU\'s commitment to achieving climate neutrality.',
      'news.eug.p2': 'A key aspect of the project is the implementation of the <strong>ISO 50001 standard</strong>, which ensures high levels of energy performance and continuous improvement in energy management systems.',
      'news.eug.p3': "SimDyns' innovative approach is expected to set new standards in energy management, significantly contributing to the EU's climate goals and sustainability objectives.",

