      'news.cyb.h4a': 'EIT Deep Tech Training and SimDyns Contribution as Pledger',
      'news.cyb.p1': '<strong>SimDyns Technology Solutions</strong> has launched an innovative <strong>AI-powered Cybersecurity Training Program</strong>, aimed at advancing skills in the deep tech sector. This program is designed to equip participants with essential knowledge and practical skills to navigate the complexities of cybersecurity in an increasingly digital world.',
      'news.cyb.p2': 'By leveraging artificial intelligence, the training offers a dynamic learning experience that prepares individuals to tackle modern cyber threats effectively.',
